"""
OIH Platform API Gateway
统一接入层：让 Qwen3-14B 调用完整生物计算工具链
Server: 192.168.31.23 | GPU0: Qwen | GPU1: Compute Tools
"""

from fastapi import FastAPI, Request
from fastapi.middleware.cors import CORSMiddleware
from fastapi.responses import JSONResponse
import uvicorn
import logging

from routers import (
    ml_tools,
    structure_prediction,
    protein_design,
    pocket_analysis,
    molecular_docking,
    md_simulation,
    pipeline,
    tasks,
)
from core.task_manager import task_manager
from core.config import settings
from qwen_agent import agent_router

logging.basicConfig(level=logging.INFO)
logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)

app = FastAPI(
    title="OIH Bio-Computing API",
    description="Unified API for AlphaFold3, RFdiffusion, ProteinMPNN, BindCraft, Fpocket, P2Rank, Vina-GPU, AutoDock-GPU, GNINA, DiffDock, GROMACS",
    version="1.0.0",
    docs_url="/docs",
    redoc_url="/redoc",
)

app.add_middleware(
    CORSMiddleware,
    allow_origins=["*"],
    allow_methods=["*"],
    allow_headers=["*"],
)

# Register all routers
app.include_router(structure_prediction.router, prefix="/api/v1/structure",    tags=["Structure Prediction"])
app.include_router(protein_design.router,       prefix="/api/v1/design",       tags=["Protein Design"])
app.include_router(pocket_analysis.router,      prefix="/api/v1/pocket",       tags=["Pocket Analysis"])
app.include_router(molecular_docking.router,    prefix="/api/v1/docking",      tags=["Molecular Docking"])
app.include_router(md_simulation.router,        prefix="/api/v1/md",           tags=["MD Simulation"])
app.include_router(pipeline.router,             prefix="/api/v1/pipeline",     tags=["Full Pipeline"])
app.include_router(ml_tools.router,          prefix="/api/v1/ml",           tags=["ML Tools"])
app.include_router(tasks.router,                prefix="/api/v1/tasks",        tags=["Task Management"])
app.include_router(agent_router,               prefix="/api/v1/agent",        tags=["AI Agent"])


@app.get("/")
async def root():
    return {
        "platform": "OIH Bio-Computing Platform",
        "version": "1.0.0",
        "server": "192.168.31.23",
        "gpu_layout": {"GPU0": "Qwen3-14B LLM", "GPU1": "Compute Tools"},
        "tools": [
            "alphafold3", "rfdiffusion", "proteinmpnn", "bindcraft",
            "fpocket", "p2rank", "vina-gpu", "autodock-gpu",
            "gnina", "diffdock", "gromacs"
        ],
        "docs": "/docs",
        "tool_definitions": "/api/v1/tool_definitions",
    }


@app.get("/api/v1/tool_definitions")
async def get_tool_definitions():
    """返回 OpenAI Function Calling 格式的工具定义，供 Qwen3-14B 直接加载"""
    from tool_definitions.qwen_tools import ALL_TOOLS
    return {"tools": ALL_TOOLS, "count": len(ALL_TOOLS)}


@app.get("/health")
async def health_check():
    from core.docker_client import check_all_containers
    container_status = await check_all_containers()
    return {
        "status": "ok",
        "task_queue": task_manager.queue_size(),
        "containers": container_status,
    }


@app.exception_handler(Exception)
async def global_exception_handler(request: Request, exc: Exception):
    logger.error(f"Unhandled exception: {exc}", exc_info=True)
    return JSONResponse(
        status_code=500,
        content={"error": str(exc), "type": type(exc).__name__}
    )


if __name__ == "__main__":
    uvicorn.run("main:app", host="0.0.0.0", port=8080, reload=False, workers=1)
